{"word":"περισσότερος","slug":"περισσότερος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>περισσότερος, τέρα, ον</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:περισσός\">περισσός</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ comp.\">comp.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:περισσός\">περισσός</a></el> ‘exceeding a standard of abundance’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> <b>greater <a href='B:470 11:9'>Mt 11:9</a>; <a href='B:470 23:13'>23:13</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:490 7:26'>Lk 7:26</a>; <a href='B:530 12:23'>1 Cor 12:23</a>, <a href='B:530 12:24'>24</a>; <a href='B:540 2:7'>2 Cor 2:7</a>; more important <a href='B:480 12:33'>Mk 12:33</a>; more severe <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vs.\">vs.</a> 40; more <a href='B:490 12:4'>Lk 12:4</a>; all the more <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vs.\">vs.</a> 48; even more <a href='B:530 15:10'>1 Cor 15:10</a>; rather in excess <a href='B:540 10:8'>2 Cor 10:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sg.\">sg.</a> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>more eagerly <a href='B:480 7:36'>Mk 7:36</a>; in reinforcement <a href='B:650 6:17'>Hb 6:17</a>; even more abundantly <a href='B:650 7:15'>7:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:περισσός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:περισσοτέρως\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}